091125001618.question: Compare the average ROI (%) and total Returns for each Investment Type across different Countries.
091125001618.agent:

  "investment type",
  "country",
  round(avg("roi (%)"), 2) as average_roi_percent,
  round(sum("returns"), 2) as total_returns
from
  parquet_scan('D:\Navaantrix\Project\poirot\data\parquet_files\1_7_finance.parquet')
group by
  "investment type",
  "country"
order by
  "investment type",
